	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I know the original MIDI Maze version had 16 players, because the protocol went through the 16 channels of the MIDI standard.<br /><br /><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/MIDI_Maze" class="postlink">According to Wikipedia</a> it did work on GameBoy too with 7 4-way adapters in series.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
